This shows how to separate the specification from implementation.

rectangle.h        class specification
rectangle.cpp      member function definitions (need to include the .h)
rectangleMain.cpp  main program using the rectangle class

Can compile separately:
g++ -c rectangle.cpp
g++ -c rectangleMain.cpp
g++ rectangle.o rectangleMain.o

Can compile all source together:
g++ rectangle.cpp rectangleMain.cpp

